########################################
            Memory
			
# free -m  (in MB)
# free -g   (in Gb)
# top (with m)    (Sort by memory usage)
# vmstat 
# vmstat -s       (displays a table of various event counters and memory statistics)
# valgrind --tool=memcheck application    (To run memcheck on an application)

